<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ emailTitle }} - Password Reset Request</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#080D4A] font-sans text-gray-800">
<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-[#7BBA29] text-white text-center p-6">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Password Reset Request</h1>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2">OpenRoaming Portal</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                To confirm your password reset request, please follow these steps:
            </p>
            <ol class="mt-4 text-lg list-decimal list-inside space-y-3">
                <li>Use the temporary password provided:
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#0045ad]">{{ currentPassword }}</span>
                </li>
                <li>Click <a class="font-bold text-[#7BBA29] underline" href="{{ absolute_url('/login/link') ~ '?' ~ 'uuid=' ~ uuid|url_encode ~ '&verificationCode=' ~ verificationCode }}">here</a> to proceed and validate your account.
                </li>
                <li>Log in using the temporary password, then set a new password.</li>
                <li>Download your OpenRoaming profile.</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
                If you did not request a password reset, please contact the support team immediately.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 text-center p-6">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Thank you,<br>
                <strong>{{ emailTitle }} Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
